All authors contributed to project and study design. T.K., N.F., K.H. participated in methodological development and implemented the network. T.K., A.B, H.Q. contributed to the comparative reconstruction analysis. T.K., A.B. and R.N. developed and implemented the acquisition sequence and protocol. R.H. and P.G.M. recruited and informed the patients. T.K., R.H. and P.G.M. performed the comparative analysis. R.B., D.R. and C.P. obtained funding, guided and supervised the project and proofread the manuscript.
